messages.message: Agreed, the empty state was actually causing other issues as well where since it only checked for not started + in progress docs, the table would disappear and then users couldn't see completed docs. I did a bandaid fix for this but i think just always showing the table is better.
@Udit can I reassign that ticket to you? It would be great if we could still show that empty state, just within the table - we want to make it clear to users that they don't have any work to do
